ğŸ” 7. Insights & Findings

Key insights derived from the analysis:

The majority of customers are non-subscribers, indicating strong potential for subscription growth

Young Adults contribute the highest share of revenue

Certain product categories significantly outperform others

High-value products present strong upselling opportunities

These insights can directly inform marketing, pricing, and customer retention strategies.
